rows.label: tlk41300022_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Gotta say I was shocked
by recent events!

rows.label: tlk41300022_02_msg0002
rows.name:
I mean, I'd heard rumors about Iira
coming to town, but I never thought
much would come of it.

rows.label: tlk41300022_02_msg0003
rows.name:
But then they went off on a rampage in
an imperial battleship, and to top it off,
destroyed our water tower!

rows.label: tlk41300022_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Anyway, I'm glad they're gone now.
The sooner the town settles back down
to its old peaceful self, the better.

rows.label: tlk41300022_02_msg0006
rows.name:
It's just a relief we didn't get involved.
If the Flamebringer couldn't even take
'em, what chance would we have had?
